59:00.498 --> 59:03.922
That was the basic theme of this was pre-World War II, of course.

59:06.906 --> 59:08.628
Nightmare stories of pogroms.

59:09.189 --> 59:11.472
I mean, I am an insomniac.

59:11.492 --> 59:12.994
I wonder why I'm an insomniac.

59:13.094 --> 59:15.377
That's the story he told us before we went to bed.

59:15.880 --> 59:18.199
I'll give you an example of a story.

